sub_title: Master in Law (LL.M) | Intellectual Property | Technology Transfer
summary: Continuous learner, outside-the-box thinker and passionate about research Lawyer holding a Colombian Master’s Degree in Law, currently finishing the LLM in Intellectual Property Law offered by the University of Turin. As a public servant with previous experience in the private sector, I work for the Secretariat of Health, Valle del Cauca Province - Colombia,  interested in looking forward to the Technology Transfer processes, setting up collaborations between public, academic, and private sector.
